{"tid":2274215,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"學生涉和你shop時拒捕 遭警扯頭撼牆兼掌摑","createTime":"2020-11-06T09:44:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-06T17:00:54.000Z","uid":56115,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"29e1848f5ee668ddc91edf6a5b8b228b06bb1d21","tid":2274215,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T09:44:16.000Z","msg":"網民在去年平安夜發起「和你shop」活動，有學生當晚被指在尖沙嘴海港城內拒捕而被拘控。案件今開審，便衣警供稱看見學生疑似擲物，表露身份後學生逃跑，他追捕時一度騎到學生背上，情況尷尬，<span class=\"red\">「我成個人擒喺佢背脊，雙腳夾住佢」</span>，其間學生扭動身軀，令他撞牆撼頭，血流披面。被告否認拒捕罪，辯方則指警方使用過份及不合理暴力。<br />\n<br />\n當日A首先從後扯首被告背囊，繼而「騎」在首被告身上，首被告因支撐不到A，失去平衡才轉動身體，很快便雙雙跌在地上，並非刻意「揈」A下來。又指A此時仍<span class=\"red\">緊箍首被告頸部</span>，首被告說「我抖唔到氣！你放手！」，但A不放手。<br />\n<br />\n將首被告帶至後巷，叫首被告跪在地上，面向牆壁，將首被告頭撼牆，再用警棍打及掌摑首被告，對首被告說羞辱的話。"},{"pid":"7c831913600ad980e73148db57ef34917190184d","tid":2274215,"uid":56115,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T09:45:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201106/PUKWRFSAZNG7TO6C4S7VCNPTLU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201106%2FPUKWRFSAZNG7TO6C4S7VCNPTLU%2F&d=q9TyM%2Fq5ITgKOQyjXL1c9u4Wvb5rKEvwepesSl%2FR16E%3D&h=144c9ba7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201106%2FPUKWRFSAZNG7TO6C4S7VCNPTLU%2F&h=177569e2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201106/PUKWRFSAZNG7TO6C4S7VCNPTLU/</a>"},{"pid":"52651b5e0799baefb3ce4fd49dd3efaa6edc6dbf","tid":2274215,"uid":356542,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T09:46:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a72075bfeb748daaf15295f7043cc180e156b5b7","tid":2274215,"uid":104425,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"52651b5e0799baefb3ce4fd49dd3efaa6edc6dbf","tid":2274215,"uid":356542,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"quote":{"pid":"29e1848f5ee668ddc91edf6a5b8b228b06bb1d21","tid":2274215,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":